WEBVTT

00:00:02.252 --> 00:00:04.504
Let's go back, Riko.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:00:17.308 --> 00:00:18.601
Riko?

00:00:20.270 --> 00:00:22.480
Alright, good job.

00:00:22.564 --> 00:00:24.357
You're dismissed.

00:00:25.275 --> 00:00:27.277
Why are you here?

00:00:28.111 --> 00:00:30.155
Why?

00:00:30.238 --> 00:00:32.032
You mean that?

00:00:33.241 --> 00:00:36.202
{\an8}I killed Satoru Gojo.

00:00:36.286 --> 00:00:37.454
Is that so?

00:00:37.537 --> 00:00:38.830
Die.

00:01:13.198 --> 00:01:14.908
Don't rush.

00:02:57.051 --> 00:03:00.221
Tombs of the Star and
the cursed warehouse are hidden barriers.

00:03:01.306 --> 00:03:03.683
You can't station people at the entrance.

00:03:04.392 --> 00:03:06.561
So once the gate's location is clear,

00:03:06.644 --> 00:03:08.062
it could easily be broken.

00:03:08.771 --> 00:03:11.441
Around this time of year,
Jujutsu sorcerers always get busy.

00:03:11.524 --> 00:03:14.944
And there are Fly Heads
everywhere in the high school.

00:03:15.028 --> 00:03:17.238
It must be chaos outside.

00:03:17.822 --> 00:03:21.159
I don't have any cursed energy,
just like an invisible man.

00:03:21.242 --> 00:03:23.453
But there's a problem.

00:03:24.662 --> 00:03:26.080
When I carry a cursed tool,

00:03:26.664 --> 00:03:29.751
the cursed enegy within the tool
will give me away.

00:03:37.884 --> 00:03:39.802
I'll continue.

00:03:41.471 --> 00:03:44.891
I have a cursed spirit
that can store items.

00:03:44.974 --> 00:03:47.560
I carry it with the cursed tools inside.

00:03:49.312 --> 00:03:50.647
I know what you're thinking.

00:03:50.730 --> 00:03:55.777
You think the cursed enegy of
the cursed spirit will give me away?

00:03:58.154 --> 00:04:02.075
I make the cursed spirit store
its own body, so it becomes smaller.

00:04:03.993 --> 00:04:06.537
Then I swallow it.

00:04:06.621 --> 00:04:09.582
An invisible man has
invisible organs, right?

00:04:10.166 --> 00:04:15.004
Now I can move freely in the barrier
carrying all the cursed tool.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:22.428
That's why I didn't use
any cursed tools at first.

00:04:25.014 --> 00:04:26.766
I had to be invisible

00:04:26.849 --> 00:04:29.769
for an surprise attack on the Six Eyes.

00:04:29.852 --> 00:04:33.106
I could kill the Star Plasma Vessel first,

00:04:33.189 --> 00:04:35.441
but the risk of being spotted
by Six Eyes is too...

00:04:35.525 --> 00:04:36.401
Enough.

00:04:36.484 --> 00:04:38.278
{\an8}It's Heavenly Restriction, right?

00:04:38.361 --> 00:04:43.366
{\an8}I know revealing information can enhance
your abilities, just like sorcerers.

00:04:43.449 --> 00:04:45.743
That's not what I asked.

00:04:47.745 --> 00:04:50.415
How did you find
the gate to the Tombs of the Star?

00:04:50.999 --> 00:04:53.501
{\an8}We didn't leave any residuals.

00:04:54.711 --> 00:04:57.797
The traces left by humans
are not just residuals.

00:04:57.880 --> 00:05:00.300
Smell, footprints.

00:05:00.383 --> 00:05:02.719
My senses are also stronger
because of the restriction.

00:05:03.428 --> 00:05:05.596
You must have met a woman on the way.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.140
What happened to her?

00:05:09.684 --> 00:05:11.185
That maid?

00:05:11.269 --> 00:05:12.603
She's probably dead.

00:05:12.687 --> 00:05:14.981
I didn't mean to kill her
nor spare her life.

00:05:15.064 --> 00:05:16.566
She'd still be alive if she's lucky.

00:05:17.275 --> 00:05:18.484
I see.

00:05:18.568 --> 00:05:19.986
Ultimately, you should...

00:05:20.069 --> 00:05:20.987
Die!

00:06:02.653 --> 00:06:04.864
<i>That's the hardest Rainbow Dragon.</i>

00:06:13.164 --> 00:06:15.083
Cursed Spirits Manipulation...

00:06:16.084 --> 00:06:17.627
Just a jumble of scraps.

00:06:30.348 --> 00:06:34.477
Say, am I... I...

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:36.437
beautiful?

00:06:37.814 --> 00:06:39.398
<i>Imaginary Cursed Spirit...</i>

00:06:39.482 --> 00:06:44.695
<i>A simple domain that makes both to be
inviolable untill I answer the question.</i>

00:06:45.571 --> 00:06:47.698
{\an8}Let me think.

00:06:47.782 --> 00:06:51.202
{\an8}I'll just be blunt at a time like this.
You're not my type.

00:06:56.666 --> 00:06:58.209
So that's how it goes.

00:07:04.048 --> 00:07:05.842
Idiot.

00:07:05.925 --> 00:07:07.343
You're doomed.

00:07:08.177 --> 00:07:09.762
You're talking about yourself.

00:07:12.932 --> 00:07:14.809
<i>Cursed Spirits Manipulation.</i>

00:07:14.892 --> 00:07:18.688
<i>The cursed technique to absorb subdued
cursed spirits and fully control them.</i>

00:07:19.564 --> 00:07:23.734
<i>If the difference is more than two levels,
I can absorb them just by subduing</i>

00:07:23.818 --> 00:07:26.195
<i>without any other condition.</i>

00:07:27.405 --> 00:07:29.073
{\an8}<i>This cursed spirit has a special ability,</i>

00:07:29.157 --> 00:07:30.700
{\an8}<i>but it is not that powerful.</i>

00:07:31.451 --> 00:07:32.869
<i>I can absorb it.</i>

00:07:32.952 --> 00:07:33.870
<i>I have his weapons.</i>

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:37.373
<i>Now I just need to defeat him by quantity...</i>

00:08:04.442 --> 00:08:07.403
Jujutsu sorcerers can't die
from these few cuts.

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:09.989
If you were a Shikigami user,
I would kill you,

00:08:10.072 --> 00:08:12.325
but you use Cursed Spirits Manipulation.

00:08:12.909 --> 00:08:16.746
I don't know what will happen to the
cursed spirits you absorbed after you die.

00:08:18.247 --> 00:08:20.708
I want to avoid trouble here.

00:08:21.417 --> 00:08:23.711
You should thank your parents.

00:08:23.794 --> 00:08:26.672
But the blessed like you

00:08:27.381 --> 00:08:31.969
still lost to me,
a monkey that can't even use Jujutsu.

00:08:32.053 --> 00:08:35.097
If you want to live longer, remember this.

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:41.103
Oh, Megumi is...

00:08:41.187 --> 00:08:42.730
I almost forgot.

00:08:42.813 --> 00:08:44.774
I named him.

00:08:49.987 --> 00:08:52.657
THE STAR RELIGIOUS GROUP HQ
HOUSE OF THE CHILDREN OF THE STAR

00:09:06.295 --> 00:09:07.838
Take it.

00:09:12.343 --> 00:09:16.472
The body of the Star Plasma Vessel,
Riko Amanai. Not a single limb is missing.

00:09:21.811 --> 00:09:23.271
Confirmed.

00:09:23.354 --> 00:09:25.898
I will pay you the agreed sum
in the way we discussed beforehand.

00:09:25.982 --> 00:09:27.233
EXECUTIVE
SHIGERU SONODA

00:09:27.316 --> 00:09:29.110
I'll give you a bit extra.

00:09:29.694 --> 00:09:32.738
The founder is truly generous with money.

00:09:32.822 --> 00:09:34.865
He's not the founder.

00:09:34.949 --> 00:09:35.825
Huh?

00:09:37.118 --> 00:09:38.661
Are you sure?

00:09:38.744 --> 00:09:41.998
You guys already helped out quite a bit,
though that were necessary expences.

00:09:42.582 --> 00:09:45.042
I even thought you'd haggle.

00:09:46.544 --> 00:09:49.964
We requested the assassination,
but we thought it was a long shot.

00:09:50.047 --> 00:09:55.303
We originated in the Nara period.
With the spread of Buddhism in Japan,

00:09:55.386 --> 00:10:00.474
Master Tengen advocated morals towards
a minority group, Jujutsu sorcerers.

00:10:01.058 --> 00:10:04.437
The realm of sorcery and
religious corporations can't get along.

00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:06.480
Born from that distortion

00:10:07.064 --> 00:10:10.985
is the current Star Religious Group's
Time Vessel Association.

00:10:11.068 --> 00:10:14.238
That's why we consistently
uphold a non-sorcerer stance.

00:10:14.947 --> 00:10:18.159
After all, even sorcerers who are allowed
to go beyond their authority

00:10:18.242 --> 00:10:20.995
cannot lay a hand on
non-sorcerers in principle.

00:10:21.704 --> 00:10:23.914
But now the time had come.

00:10:24.749 --> 00:10:28.794
The taboo recorded in our scriptures,

00:10:28.878 --> 00:10:32.715
merging of something impure
and the very person

00:10:32.798 --> 00:10:36.636
we the Star Religious Group worship
as a monotheistic religion.

00:10:38.888 --> 00:10:40.306
In front of the believers,

00:10:40.389 --> 00:10:43.267
if we turn a blind eye to merging,
we won't be able to continue.

00:10:44.226 --> 00:10:48.522
But if we interfere too much,
we might be eliminated by the sorcerers.

00:10:49.106 --> 00:10:52.276
We were desparate.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:54.654
But now?

00:10:54.737 --> 00:10:56.989
We now hold in our hands

00:10:57.073 --> 00:10:59.116
everything we could have lost.

00:10:59.700 --> 00:11:02.495
That's why we're so
generous with our money.

00:11:04.538 --> 00:11:06.749
If Tengen loses control,

00:11:06.832 --> 00:11:10.127
the one who won't be able to continue
might be the human society.

00:11:12.213 --> 00:11:15.508
If we are to fall with the star,
that's the way it is.

00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:30.731
You said they helped out.
Were you referring to Okinawa?

00:11:30.815 --> 00:11:32.066
Yes.

00:11:32.149 --> 00:11:35.027
Why didn't you kill the maid then?

00:11:35.111 --> 00:11:36.529
Didn't I tell you?

00:11:36.612 --> 00:11:40.533
<i>Take her somewhere far away and kill her.</i>

00:11:41.117 --> 00:11:44.995
Because at that time,
I had roughly understood your plan.

00:11:45.579 --> 00:11:48.040
I thought the relief of successfully
rescuing the maid would

00:11:48.124 --> 00:11:52.461
further weaken that guy's spirit compared
with the tension of failing to save her.

00:11:52.545 --> 00:11:58.342
Don't you often give vague orders
to keep the other party in the dark?

00:11:58.426 --> 00:12:00.594
At the end, it worked out perfectly.

00:12:00.678 --> 00:12:03.889
Stop pushing me around. I'm just an agent.

00:12:03.973 --> 00:12:06.475
But why Okinawa?

00:12:08.727 --> 00:12:10.896
That was pretty funny.

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:14.024
You usually use a car
to transfer captives, right?

00:12:14.108 --> 00:12:17.194
Public transportation is too risky.

00:12:17.778 --> 00:12:22.575
I heard that was the
chairman's private plane.

00:12:22.658 --> 00:12:24.618
Still, it wasn't necessary.

00:12:26.787 --> 00:12:29.707
Rich people think differently.

00:12:29.790 --> 00:12:32.001
Let's use this money to have a meal.

00:12:32.084 --> 00:12:34.670
Take me to the place where
you usually entertain clients.

00:12:35.629 --> 00:12:38.549
No. I know you don't treat men.

00:12:40.092 --> 00:12:42.511
I've decided a long time ago.

00:12:42.595 --> 00:12:46.098
Besides work and going to hell,
I don't want to get involved with you.

00:13:07.077 --> 00:13:09.538
Hi, long time no see.

00:13:11.081 --> 00:13:12.082
Seriously?

00:13:12.666 --> 00:13:14.460
Absolutely.

00:13:15.169 --> 00:13:17.254
Fit as a fiddle.

00:13:17.963 --> 00:13:19.507
Reverse Cursed Technique.

00:13:20.424 --> 00:13:21.759
Correct.

00:13:21.842 --> 00:13:24.386
<i>The moment you pierced my throat,</i>

00:13:24.470 --> 00:13:28.724
<i>I gave up on fighting back and focused
on activating Reverse Cursed Technique.</i>

00:13:29.391 --> 00:13:34.605
<i>Cursed energy is negative energy. It can
strengthen the body but not regenerate.</i>

00:13:34.688 --> 00:13:39.151
<i>So, multiplying two kinds of negative
energy to produce positive energy.</i>

00:13:39.235 --> 00:13:40.945
<i>That's the Reverse Cursed Technique.</i>

00:13:41.529 --> 00:13:45.157
It sounds simple,
but I had never succeeded before.

00:13:45.241 --> 00:13:49.203
- And I couldn't understand what...
-<i>He's rambling.</i>

00:13:49.286 --> 00:13:50.663
<i>Is he...</i>

00:13:50.746 --> 00:13:52.665
<i>high?</i>

00:13:52.748 --> 00:13:55.417
But before my death, I mastered

00:13:55.501 --> 00:13:57.419
the core of cursed energy.

00:13:57.503 --> 00:14:04.426
You failed because you didn't behead me
or use that cursed tool to stab my head.

00:14:05.386 --> 00:14:07.054
I failed?

00:14:09.682 --> 00:14:11.517
The battle is just about to begin.

00:14:12.101 --> 00:14:17.231
Is it? Yeah. Maybe!

00:14:30.578 --> 00:14:32.663
<i>Cursed Technique Reversal.</i>

00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:35.666
<i>Red.</i>

00:14:50.556 --> 00:14:51.849
That monster.

00:14:59.106 --> 00:15:00.691
<i>Looks like my bones weren't shattered.</i>

00:15:01.400 --> 00:15:04.820
{\an8}<i>That shockwave just now is
Limitless Cursed Technique,</i>

00:15:04.904 --> 00:15:06.322
{\an8}<i>Cursed Technique Reversal, Red.</i>

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:10.951
<i>He injeceted the positive energy
of the Reverse Cursed Technique</i>

00:15:11.535 --> 00:15:16.165
<i>into the Limitless Cursed
Technique etched on the body.</i>

00:15:16.248 --> 00:15:18.626
<i>First, force of stopping.</i>

00:15:18.709 --> 00:15:21.045
<i>The neutral Limitless
Cursed Technique.</i>

00:15:22.087 --> 00:15:24.340
<i>Second, force of attraction.</i>

00:15:24.423 --> 00:15:26.842
<i>The enhanced Limitless
Cursed Technique, Blue.</i>

00:15:28.218 --> 00:15:32.681
<i>Third, force of repulsion.
Cursed Technique Reversal, Red.</i>

00:15:35.351 --> 00:15:38.395
<i>All fine with me.</i>

00:15:40.356 --> 00:15:41.315
<i>Something's wrong.</i>

00:15:47.196 --> 00:15:48.364
<i>Something's wrong.</i>

00:15:51.533 --> 00:15:53.285
No, it's good.

00:15:55.829 --> 00:15:57.122
I'll kill you.

00:16:17.142 --> 00:16:19.353
<i>I'm sorry, Amanai.</i>

00:16:20.062 --> 00:16:23.399
<i>I'm not angry because of you right now.</i>

00:16:24.775 --> 00:16:26.819
<i>And I don't hate anyone.</i>

00:16:28.988 --> 00:16:31.532
<i>Right now, it's just that</i>

00:16:31.615 --> 00:16:34.284
<i>this world feels so good.</i>

00:16:50.968 --> 00:16:53.929
Above and below, only I dominate.

00:16:57.391 --> 00:17:02.187
<i>The advantage of techniques passed down
is there are instructions for use.</i>

00:17:03.147 --> 00:17:07.067
<i>The disadvantage is that the technique
information is easily leaked.</i>

00:17:07.651 --> 00:17:11.113
<i>You're from the Zenin Family, aren't you?</i>

00:17:11.196 --> 00:17:14.116
<i>That's why you know so much
about the Limitless Cursed Technique.</i>

00:17:16.243 --> 00:17:17.995
<i>But this one,</i>

00:17:18.078 --> 00:17:21.540
<i>only a very few people in
the Gojo family know it.</i>

00:17:32.843 --> 00:17:34.762
<i>Lapse and reversal.</i>

00:17:34.845 --> 00:17:37.973
<i>Their infinities collide</i>

00:17:38.057 --> 00:17:40.559
<i>and release the imaginary
mass generated from the collision.</i>

00:17:40.642 --> 00:17:42.519
<i>Hollow Purple.</i>

00:17:52.279 --> 00:17:53.822
<i>Something's wrong.</i>

00:17:55.199 --> 00:17:57.826
<i>I don't work for free.</i>

00:17:57.910 --> 00:18:00.662
<i>I would usually say this and then leave.</i>

00:18:02.247 --> 00:18:07.377
<i>But what appeared in front of me is an
awakened Limitless Cursed Technique user.</i>

00:18:07.461 --> 00:18:11.256
<i>And at this moment, he might have become
the strongest sorcerer in modern times.</i>

00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:15.719
<i>I suddenly wanted to deny and overturn</i>

00:18:15.803 --> 00:18:20.724
<i>the Zenin Family that denied me,
the realm of sorcery, and its apex.</i>

00:18:21.683 --> 00:18:24.103
<i>To assert myself,</i>

00:18:24.186 --> 00:18:26.730
<i>I did something I usually don't.</i>

00:18:28.023 --> 00:18:30.609
<i>From that moment, I had already lost.</i>

00:18:40.661 --> 00:18:43.038
<i>Haven't I already given up my pride?</i>

00:18:44.081 --> 00:18:50.712
<i>Not respecting myself or others.
Isn't that the way of life I chose?</i>

00:18:54.842 --> 00:18:57.136
Do you have any last words?

00:19:00.347 --> 00:19:01.598
No.

00:19:13.152 --> 00:19:15.279
In two or three years,

00:19:15.362 --> 00:19:17.865
my child will be sold to the Zenin Family.

00:19:18.824 --> 00:19:21.076
Do as you please.

00:21:20.404 --> 00:21:22.155
Mom.

00:21:22.864 --> 00:21:25.200
Hug.

00:22:03.613 --> 00:22:05.824
You took your time, Suguru.

00:22:05.907 --> 00:22:08.035
No, I guess it was quick.

00:22:08.618 --> 00:22:12.664
{\an8}There are so many facilities
of the Star Religious Group in Tokyo.

00:22:13.915 --> 00:22:16.293
{\an8}You're Satoru... right?

00:22:17.377 --> 00:22:19.296
What happened?

00:22:19.379 --> 00:22:21.882
You've seen Shoko, right?

00:22:21.965 --> 00:22:25.761
Yes, she healed me. I'm fine.

00:22:29.056 --> 00:22:32.309
No, even if I'm fine,
it doesn't help anything.

00:22:32.392 --> 00:22:35.687
I messed up. It's not your fault.

00:22:36.897 --> 00:22:37.773
Let's go back.

00:22:38.482 --> 00:22:39.316
Suguru.

00:22:39.900 --> 00:22:42.652
Should we kill these people?

00:22:42.736 --> 00:22:46.073
I probably wouldn't
feel anything right now.

00:22:48.325 --> 00:22:50.827
No need. It's meaningless.

00:22:51.661 --> 00:22:55.373
They look like just ordinary believers.

00:22:55.457 --> 00:22:59.336
The main culprit who knows the realm of
sorcery should have already run away.

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:04.466
Unlike the bounty,
they can't argue in this situation.

00:23:04.549 --> 00:23:06.843
This group is inherently problematic.

00:23:07.427 --> 00:23:09.221
It will probably disintegrate soon.

00:23:11.014 --> 00:23:12.099
Meaning, huh?

00:23:12.808 --> 00:23:15.602
Do we really need that?

00:23:27.447 --> 00:23:29.116
It's important.

00:23:29.950 --> 00:23:33.286
Especially for sorcerers.

00:23:36.289 --> 00:23:40.752
<i>The person who first said the unexpected
aspect, did they think humans are cubes?</i>

00:23:40.836 --> 00:23:45.507
<i>And the person who first called someone
flimsy, did they think humans are flat?</i>

00:23:45.590 --> 00:23:47.676
<i>Next Episode, Premature Death</i>

00:23:47.759 --> 00:23:50.762
<i>Either way, there are front and back.</i>

00:23:51.305 --> 00:24:51.356
